Class AccessControlStRow

java.lang.Object
  core.data.dto.CoreDto
      dataObjects.privacyService.AccessControlStRow
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class AccessControlStRow
extends core.data.dto.CoreDto

AccessControlStRows class NOTE: This class holds a row for access control module (i.e. a row each from ac_access_control_mgr, ac_access_restrictions, ac_action_to_take and ac_hide_info table). This class was written so as we can use a single database query and get row appropriate to statement_id from all the above listed tables.

NeerajR.
